Class PersonPersonTypeHelper

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.ofbiz.commonapp.person.PersonPersonTypeHelper
public class PersonPersonTypeHelper
extends java.lang.Object

Title: Person Component - Person Person Type Entity

Description: Maps a Person to a Person Type; necessary so a person can be of multiple types.

The Helper class from the PersonPersonType Entity EJB; acts as a proxy for the Home interface
